front.title: •Sil Unch
front.gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While aboard a battleship, that battleship is immune to attrition < 4 and draws a battle destiny if not able to otherwise.
front.lore: Neimoidian Trade Federation Droid Control Ship officer. Specialized in battle droid control programming and interfaces. Does not enjoy being commanded by Daultay Dofine.
